{
  "stem": "894.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He had four absolutely gorgeous children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the way they brought them up was like you would think of-- of the royal family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "This is how these children were brought up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he was alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So we moved in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He reopened his business.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He said, now that you're here, there is somebody to do it for.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, sure.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, because he was maybe 26, 27 years old when he got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I wasn't even born then, obviously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And so we went about it there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tried to get a little education.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went to this professor, this English professor and took English lessons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But rumors started flying that you can't walk the streets-- that the Russians are raping girls, and that you'll-- they'd get drunk.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so it got to a point where we were afraid to leave the house.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we decided it doesn't make much sense to stay.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the reason we didn't go back home, because we had from our hometown some friends visiting us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They found out we were in my sister's house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said they were home-- nobody, nobody, not a sign of anybody.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we urged our brother-in-law to make the decision to leave everything and just go with us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And there was-- he had a nephew-- a young man-- his brother's son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he didn't want to go with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He later on had a lot of problems getting out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took many, many years to get him out of there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But my brother-in-law took our advice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We paid somebody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We paid someone to smuggle us out during the night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was already not easy to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
